<i>[Harry] In Jordan,
locals believe</i>

03:50.231 --> 03:53.465
<i>the video has captured
something supernatural.</i>

03:54.867 --> 03:57.936
<i>[Jeff] In this region, and
really, across the whole world,</i>

03:57.938 --> 04:02.241
there's a belief in this supernatural
or even preternatural power.

04:02.243 --> 04:03.242
For many,

04:03.244 --> 04:05.644
