Aladdin, Arabian Nights.

04:16.823 --> 04:19.124
<i>[Harry] Djinn are not
the lamp-dwelling,</i>

04:19.126 --> 04:22.294
<i>wish-granting servants
from Hollywood films.</i>

04:23.296 --> 04:26.231
They're widely known
to be shapeshifters

04:26.233 --> 04:28.533
and have other sorts
of superhuman powers.

04:28.535 --> 04:30.535
[distorted wailing]

04:30.537 --> 04:31.837
Basically, in short,

04:31.839 --> 04:33.805
demons.

04:33.807 --> 04:38.043
<i>[Harry] The Quran tells
believers that djinn are real.</i>

04:38.045 --> 04:39.278
<i>[Craig] Some don't even
want to talk about it.</i>

04:39.280 --> 04:41.179
They won't even
<i>mention the word djinn</i>

04:41.181 --> 04:43.682
<i>because they feel that
the djinn derives its energy</i>

04:43.684 --> 04:45.284
<i>from human attention.</i>

04:46.419 --> 04:47.953
If you live in the area

04:47.955 --> 04:49.855
and you see something
like this on the road,

04:49.857 --> 04:51.189
<i>you're going to think, djinn.</i>

04:51.958 --> 04:53.025
[throaty screeching]

04:53.027 --> 04:54.126
[yelling]

04:56.129 --> 04:57.829
[static]

04:57.831 --> 05:00.499
[Islamic music]

05:00.501 --> 05:02.701
