05:29.029 --> 05:30.996
<i>that in 2009,</i>

05:30.998 --> 05:34.800
<i>the Saudi state launched
its own anti witchcraft unit</i>

05:34.802 --> 05:36.968
<i>to tackle the problem.</i>

05:36.970 --> 05:40.706
<i>The puritanical police force
claimed to catch witches,</i>

05:40.708 --> 05:44.076
<i>often after a tip off
from a member of the public.</i>

05:44.243 --> 05:45.877
<i>[Rhonda] In 2011,</i>

05:45.879 --> 05:49.815
a Saudi woman was beheaded
for practicing sorcery.

05:49.817 --> 05:54.052
In general, these people who are
accused of being witches are not.

05:54.054 --> 05:57.022
They've just been set up
by irate neighbors

05:57.024 --> 06:01.059
or implicated in some
sting operation.

06:01.061 --> 06:03.695
<i>[Harry] But the authorities
report genuine cases</i>

06:03.697 --> 06:07.032
<i>of people who claim
to practice black magic.</i>

06:07.034 --> 06:10.335
In one raid, the investigators
were confronted

06:10.337 --> 06:12.137
by a naked sorceress.

06:12.872 --> 06:14.372
[woman screaming]

06:14.374 --> 06:17.409
<i>[Harry] The sorceress is said to
have escaped out of the window.</i>

06:18.177 --> 06:20.912
<i>Incredibly, investigators report</i>

06:20.914 --> 06:22.948
<i>that she flew out like a bird.</i>

06:24.083 --> 06:27.119
<i>The woman may have
been in a trance-like state,</i>

06:27.121 --> 06:29.254
<i>making her feel
like she could fly.</i>

06:29.256 --> 06:31.890
[distorted music]

06:31.892 --> 06:34.793
<i>[Harry] Anthropologists
have found that sorcerers,</i>

06:34.795 --> 06:37.696
<i>priests and warriors
