06:46.673 --> 06:49.274
<i>to be possessed
by spirits or animals.</i>

06:49.276 --> 06:52.210
<i>And as a result,
are capable of extraordinary,</i>

06:52.212 --> 06:54.012
<i>inhuman feats.</i>

06:54.014 --> 06:56.181
Maybe they really
do have some power,

06:56.183 --> 06:59.184
some ability that we don't have.

07:00.920 --> 07:03.121
<i>[Harry] A University
of Pennsylvania study</i>

07:03.123 --> 07:05.257
<i>found the frontal lobe
of the brain,</i>

07:05.259 --> 07:08.827
<i>the part that directs
conscious, rational behavior,</i>

07:08.829 --> 07:12.464
<i>diminishes as people
enter a trance-like state.</i>

07:13.232 --> 07:14.466
<i>The figure in the footage</i>

07:14.468 --> 07:17.369
<i>could be in a similar
psychological state,</i>

07:17.371 --> 07:19.704
<i>advancing aggressively
on a vehicle</i>

07:19.706 --> 07:22.374
<i>because she believes herself
to be invincible.</i>

07:24.944 --> 07:26.044
The car keeps reversing

07:26.279 --> 07:28.880
