07:47.033 --> 07:50.035
<i>[Harry] And,
heading for a beautiful beach,</i>

07:50.037 --> 07:53.438
<i>a titanic tentacle
dripping with poison.</i>

07:53.440 --> 07:54.906
<i>[Jayde] Forget about Jaws.</i>

07:54.908 --> 07:57.008
This giant is the new definition

07:57.010 --> 07:58.343
of horror from the deep.

07:58.345 --> 08:00.212
[underwater currents]

08:00.780 --> 08:02.247
[static]

08:06.819 --> 08:09.154
<i>[Harry] Two travelers in Jordan</i>

08:09.156 --> 08:11.656
<i>are attacked
by a demonic-looking woman.</i>

08:13.326 --> 08:15.961
- [throaty screeching]
- [yelling in foreign language]

